{"tid":1326211,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"【 突發 721重要通知 】民陣集會改遊行往終審法院","createTime":"2019-07-17T06:38:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-18T02:47:06.000Z","uid":168555,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"a32b417efdd19db50f53a6281951d058a67f56d7","tid":1326211,"uid":168555,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T06:38:30.000Z","msg":"【 721重要通知 】<br />\n<br />\n經過兩日商討，民陣有信心721遊行會取得不反對通知書。以下為最新的行動安排︰<br />\n<br />\n獨立調查 捍衛法治 守護真相 重申五大訴求<br />\n2019年7月21日（日）<br />\n下午3時維園集合起步，往終審法院，在遮打道結束遊行<br />\n<br />\n====Q&amp;A====<br />\n1. 為何將集會改遊行？<br />\n民陣得悉原定各區地區遊行日期都有所更改，並考慮到近日局勢，認為改為遊行較為適當。<br />\n<br />\n2. 為何將終點定在中環？<br />\n今次遊行，重中之重的訴求是要求成立由法官主持的獨立調查委員會，我們認為遊行到終審法院正義女神像前，突顯我們的訴求，正是為了捍衛香港的法治。<br />\n<br />\n3. 民陣721後會有其他行動嗎？<br />\n目前可以預視到的行動包括在8月31日（人大831決定五周年）、10月1日等，民間有意發起與五大訴求相關行動。<br />\n<br />\n至於其他時間，則視乎局勢發展，尤其是林鄭月娥政府的回應。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rxC0nGS.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrxC0nGS.jpg&h=7fabeced&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0cfd246ba3b684dc20a9890a9b9f96c97e02a1ef","tid":1326211,"uid":83198,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T06:39:32.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">7。21 港島見</span><br />\n請帶齊裝備<br />\n唔好再靜係帶口罩 要保護自己 <br />\n<br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">光 復 香 港 。 時 代 革 命 。 香 港 建 國</code></pre>"},{"pid":"6a48da9572e1e544932081021ce4c094262b4237","tid":1326211,"uid":199727,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T19:23:09.000Z","msg":"721見"},{"pid":"e1da958c81aa214217c172cdb7cc2d80dd8fc2f9","tid":1326211,"uid":122988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T19:29:09.000Z","msg":"半夜三更一定要推721post"},{"pid":"929dce81e87878093b8380e485d5e356488c57ee","tid":1326211,"uid":156582,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T19:51:36.000Z","msg":"721見"},{"pid":"892c4f39ea8790628b6159b160ec5a9f82d11ed1","tid":1326211,"uid":228244,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T02:34:47.000Z","msg":"今次著乜嘢色衫?"},{"pid":"2686327882b06bc0caf169faf9bfb9122423d34c","tid":1326211,"uid":248290,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T02:37:41.000Z","msg":"721見<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dVibA2b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdVibA2b.jpg&h=3792062a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b9a8bbab086e870f1a39ed01b6e31f63d28a89cf","tid":1326211,"uid":275588,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T02:39:31.000Z","msg":"PUHS"},{"pid":"64f94579200cf6f44d6d83246882813dc0dd2b5f","tid":1326211,"uid":42799,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T02:39:54.000Z","msg":"Pish"},{"pid":"a2efee7033a8213e1dc14e8f6f7804c7db9887cd","tid":1326211,"uid":129878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T02:40:11.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"609fc78e0c1148bc766ced065f52498421bbd006","tid":1326211,"uid":259611,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T02:47:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}